{
  "chapter": 12,
  "title": "春水俪影",
  "raw_dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "兰兰",
      "text": "小姐，你看这蝴蝶美不美？",
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "这蝴蝶是你捉来的？",
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "兰兰",
      "text": "嗯，我捉了很久，好不容易才捉到，幸好没有把它的翅膀弄断。",
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你虽然没有弄断它的翅膀，却弄死了它。你心里不难受？",
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "兰兰",
      "text": "蝴蝶反正很快就会死的。",
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "人也反正很快就会死的，是不是？",
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "兰兰",
      "text": "可是……可是……",
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "可是怎么样？蝴蝶有没有伤害过你？",
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "兰兰",
      "text": "没有。",
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "蝴蝶有没有伤害过任何东西？",
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "兰兰",
      "text": "没有。",
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "那你为什么要伤害它？",
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "兰兰",
      "text": "我去捉它，只不过是因为它很美，很好看……",
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "兰兰",
      "text": "我其实并不想伤害它。",
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你虽然不想伤害它，但它已死在你手上。",
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "兰兰",
      "text": "但现在它还是和活着时同样美丽，我若没有去捉它，它现在也许已经死在阴沟里，也许已被吃进了蜘蛛的肚子。",
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "兰兰",
      "text": "小姐，水已快凉了，你快去洗吧！晚上你不是还要出去吗？",
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "兰兰",
      "text": "小姐，脸洗好了吧！花公子一定等得快要疯了。",
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "让他等，让他疯。",
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "兰兰",
      "text": "小姐你难道一点也不喜欢他？",
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "兰兰",
      "text": "那么小姐最近为什么总是跟他一起出去玩呢？",
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "也许只因为没有人来约我。",
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "醉汉",
      "text": "你在等人？",
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "醉汉",
      "text": "我也等过人，但要是值得等的人，我才等，你的呢？",
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花公子",
      "text": "你管不着。",
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "醉汉",
      "text": "我当然管不着，但你等的若是个婊子，那就太冤枉了。",
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花公子",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "醉汉",
      "text": "你等的不是婊子？难道还会是个皇后？",
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花公子",
      "text": "是又怎样？",
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "醉汉",
      "text": "她也许是你的皇后，却是我的婊子。",
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花公子",
      "text": "你莫非知道我等的是谁？",
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "醉汉",
      "text": "你等的是小蝶，是不是？",
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花公子",
      "text": "你认得她？",
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "醉汉",
      "text": "我怎会不认得，她既是你的皇后，也是我的婊子。",
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "醉汉",
      "text": "这样才好些了，但我还可以让你变得更好些。",
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_gong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "花公子",
      "text": "你……你为什么要对付我？",
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "醉汉",
      "text": "因为她是我的婊子，我一个人的婊子，不是你的。",
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你是不是想死？",
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你活过吗？",
      "line_start": 435,
      "line_end": 435
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你没有死？",
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "一个人若连活都没有活过，怎么能死？",
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你什么时候来的？",
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "该来的时候就来了。",
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "该来的时候？",
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我总觉得好像欠你一点什么，所以……",
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你认为我救过你，所以也该救我一次，是不是？",
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "老实说，我从未想到你这样的人也有想死的时候。",
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你一向都是这么说话的么？",
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我只说真话。",
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "真话有时是很伤人的。",
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "谎话也许会不伤人，但却伤人的心。",
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "那么我问你，那天我若不来，你是不是真的会死？",
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我只想死……想不想死，我会不会死是两回事。",
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "两回事？",
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "很多人，都想死，很多人，都没有死。",
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "所以我并没有救你，你也没有救我。",
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "真正要死的人，本就是谁都救不了的。",
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "所以你不欠我，我也不欠你的。",
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我欠你。",
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "欠我什么？",
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我现在已不想死。",
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "这么样说，我也欠你。",
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "欠我什么？",
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我想不到今天晚上能笑得出来。",
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你喜欢笑？",
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "喜不喜欢笑，和笑不笑得出来也是两回事。",
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你看到我才笑的？",
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你认为我这人很滑稽？",
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "不是滑稽，是有趣。",
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "那么，你为什么不陪我喝两杯酒去？",
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "谁说我不去？",
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我不喜欢敬别人的酒。",
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我也不喜欢别人敬我的酒。",
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "但是，我更不喜欢别人喝得少。",
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "喝酒的人都有这种毛病，总希望别人先醉……就算他自己想喝醉，也希望别人先醉。",
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你对喝醉的人，好像了解得很多。",
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "因为我也是其中之一。",
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "看来你也不喜欢说谎。",
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "那只因为我对你没有说谎的必要。",
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "若是有必要呢？",
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "有必要时，我时常说谎，而且说出来的谎话有时连我自己都不信。",
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "要怎样才算有必要呢？",
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "那样的情形很多。",
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "譬如说……",
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "譬如说，你若看上了我，已让我知道你在喜欢我……",
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "为什么不可能？",
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "因为……我们彼此根本不了解，甚至可以说不认识。",
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "但，我们现在已经认识了，何况……了不了解是一回事，喜不喜欢又是另一回事，我相信了解你的人一定不会多，喜欢你的人一定不会少。",
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你这是在恭维我，还是在讽刺我？",
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我只不过说出了我心里想说的话。",
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你常常在别人面前说出你心里想说的话？",
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我从不说……",
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "可是今天你……",
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "今天是例外，对你是例外。",
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我也不知道。",
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你的毛病是话说得太多，酒喝得太少。",
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我在等你。",
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "等我？",
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你已经比我少喝了两杯了。",
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你要我喝得跟你一样？",
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你想灌醉我？",
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "的确有这意思。",
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "那么我警告你，要灌醉我并不容易。",
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "就因为不容易，所以才有趣，越不容易越有趣。",
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我忽然发现跟你在一起，不但话说得特别多，酒也喝得特别多。",
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "一个人只有跟老朋友在一起的时候，才会这样的，是不是？",
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "是。",
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "但我们并不是老朋友。",
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我们不是。",
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "听说你酒喝得越多，眼睛越亮，是不是？",
      "line_start": 643,
      "line_end": 643
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你对我还知道多少？",
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我知道你酒量很好，知道别人都叫你小蝶。",
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "还有呢？",
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "没有了。",
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我却连你叫什么都不知道。",
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我姓孟……",
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我并不想知道你的名字，因为我们之间根本没有任何关系，以前没有，以后更不会有。",
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "因为我不高兴。",
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 664
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你要走？",
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我早就该走了。",
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我送你。",
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "不必，不必，不必……",
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我自己有腿，我的腿并没有断。",
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "以后……",
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "以后？我们没有以后，以后你还是不认识我，我也不认识你。",
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你就这样让我走？",
      "line_start": 692,
      "line_end": 692
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我还能怎么样？",
      "line_start": 694,
      "line_end": 694
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你不想留住我？",
      "line_start": 696,
      "line_end": 696
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "若是别人，一定会想尽法子留下我。",
      "line_start": 699,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我不是别人，我就是我。",
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 702
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你这人真有趣，真有趣……",
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 706
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你已经有点醉了。",
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你不喜欢我醉？——男人都喜欢女人喝醉，女人喝醉了时，男人才有机会占便宜。",
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我不要回去，就不要回去……",
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 720
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "昨天晚上我是不是喝醉了？",
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 730
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "每个人都有喝醉的时候。",
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 734
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我平常本不会那么快就喝醉的。",
      "line_start": 736,
      "line_end": 736
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我知道你昨天心情不好。",
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 738
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你知道？",
      "line_start": 740,
      "line_end": 740
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "心情好的人，绝不会一个人跑到河边去想死。",
      "line_start": 742,
      "line_end": 742
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我喝醉了后，说了些什么话？",
      "line_start": 744,
      "line_end": 746
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你说你不想回去。",
      "line_start": 748,
      "line_end": 748
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "然后呢？",
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 750
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "然后你就没有回去。",
      "line_start": 752,
      "line_end": 752
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我……我没有说别的？",
      "line_start": 754,
      "line_end": 754
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你以为自己会说什么？",
      "line_start": 756,
      "line_end": 756
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "现在我真的该回去了。",
      "line_start": 758,
      "line_end": 760
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你……你用不着送我。",
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "line_start": 766,
      "line_end": 766
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你为什么一直瞪着我？",
      "line_start": 768,
      "line_end": 768
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "因为我怕。",
      "line_start": 770,
      "line_end": 770
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "怕？怕什么？",
      "line_start": 772,
      "line_end": 772
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "怕以后再也看不到你！",
      "line_start": 774,
      "line_end": 774
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我希望以后还能够去找你。",
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 780
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "不行。",
      "line_start": 782,
      "line_end": 782
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你若去找我，一定会后悔的。",
      "line_start": 786,
      "line_end": 786
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "后悔？",
      "line_start": 788,
      "line_end": 788
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我对你不会有好处，我对任何人都没有好处，无论谁遇到我都会倒楣的。",
      "line_start": 790,
      "line_end": 790
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "那是我的事，我只问你……我只问你，你愿不愿意我再去找你？",
      "line_start": 792,
      "line_end": 794
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你绝不能去找我。",
      "line_start": 796,
      "line_end": 796
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "但我以后却说不定会来找你。",
      "line_start": 800,
      "line_end": 800
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你猜我带了什么东西来？",
      "line_start": 844,
      "line_end": 846
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我忽然想到既然吃了你一顿，至少也该还请你一次，是不是？",
      "line_start": 850,
      "line_end": 850
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你饿不饿？",
      "line_start": 854,
      "line_end": 854
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我饿得简直可以吞下一匹马。",
      "line_start": 856,
      "line_end": 858
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我已有很久没有这样躺在草地上了，你呢？",
      "line_start": 868,
      "line_end": 868
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我常常躺在地上，但今天却觉得有点不同。",
      "line_start": 870,
      "line_end": 870
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "什么不同？",
      "line_start": 872,
      "line_end": 872
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "今天的草好像特别柔软。",
      "line_start": 874,
      "line_end": 874
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "原来你也很会说话，说得很好听。",
      "line_start": 876,
      "line_end": 876
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "真话有时也很好听的，有时甚至比谎话还好听。",
      "line_start": 878,
      "line_end": 878
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你有没有想过？",
      "line_start": 880,
      "line_end": 880
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "想过什么？",
      "line_start": 882,
      "line_end": 882
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "想过我是不是会再来找你？",
      "line_start": 884,
      "line_end": 884
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我想过。",
      "line_start": 886,
      "line_end": 886
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你以为我不会再来了，是不是？",
      "line_start": 888,
      "line_end": 888
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我的确是没有想到，你来得这么快。",
      "line_start": 890,
      "line_end": 890
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你知不知道我为什么这么快就又来了？",
      "line_start": 892,
      "line_end": 892
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我不知道，我只知道你走了以后，我忽然觉得很寂寞。",
      "line_start": 894,
      "line_end": 894
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "也许我们还不是朋友，但也不知为了什么，我只有跟你在一起的时候，才会觉得不再寂寞。",
      "line_start": 906,
      "line_end": 906
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "无论如何，我既已来了，你就该好好地陪我玩一天。",
      "line_start": 914,
      "line_end": 916
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我陪你——无论你想做什么，我都愿陪你。",
      "line_start": 918,
      "line_end": 918
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我们去掘宝，好不好？",
      "line_start": 920,
      "line_end": 922
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "掘宝？",
      "line_start": 924,
      "line_end": 924
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我知道这树林里有个地方，埋着宝藏。",
      "line_start": 926,
      "line_end": 926
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "这树林里不但有宝藏，还有神仙，几百个大大小小的神仙，有的还喜欢把人变成骡子，你可得当心。",
      "line_start": 928,
      "line_end": 928
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我说的话你不信？",
      "line_start": 930,
      "line_end": 930
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我说的话你信不信？",
      "line_start": 932,
      "line_end": 932
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你不信，我带你去找，找到了，看你还信不信？",
      "line_start": 936,
      "line_end": 936
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我闻到了。",
      "line_start": 940,
      "line_end": 940
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "闻到了什么？",
      "line_start": 942,
      "line_end": 942
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "宝藏的味道。",
      "line_start": 944,
      "line_end": 944
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "哦？在哪里？",
      "line_start": 946,
      "line_end": 946
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "宝藏就在这里，就在你睡的地方下面。",
      "line_start": 948,
      "line_end": 948
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "这下面有宝藏？",
      "line_start": 950,
      "line_end": 950
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你还是不信？",
      "line_start": 952,
      "line_end": 952
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我若掘出来了呢？",
      "line_start": 956,
      "line_end": 956
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你若掘得出来，你就去找个神仙来把我变成骡子。",
      "line_start": 958,
      "line_end": 958
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "好，男子汉大丈夫说出来的话可不能不算数。",
      "line_start": 960,
      "line_end": 960
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "看来有个人要变成驴子了。",
      "line_start": 966,
      "line_end": 968
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我上当了，这酒坛一定是你刚才埋下去的。",
      "line_start": 974,
      "line_end": 976
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "那不管，我只问你，这算不算是宝藏？",
      "line_start": 978,
      "line_end": 978
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "当然算，我简直想不出天下还有什么比这更好的宝藏。",
      "line_start": 980,
      "line_end": 982
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "宝藏已有了，骡子呢？",
      "line_start": 984,
      "line_end": 984
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "骡子就在你的面前，你难道没有看见？",
      "line_start": 986,
      "line_end": 986
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "这骡子好像只有两条腿。",
      "line_start": 988,
      "line_end": 988
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "两条腿的骡子，比四条腿的好。",
      "line_start": 990,
      "line_end": 992
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "怎么好？",
      "line_start": 994,
      "line_end": 994
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "两条腿的骡子能喝酒。",
      "line_start": 996,
      "line_end": 996
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我要回去了。",
      "line_start": 1020,
      "line_end": 1020
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你要怎样？",
      "line_start": 1028,
      "line_end": 1028
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你故意假装听不见我的话是不是？",
      "line_start": 1030,
      "line_end": 1030
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我为什么要假装听不见？",
      "line_start": 1032,
      "line_end": 1034
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我说我要回去。",
      "line_start": 1036,
      "line_end": 1036
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "这次你听见了吗？",
      "line_start": 1038,
      "line_end": 1040
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我听见了！",
      "line_start": 1042,
      "line_end": 1042
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你有什么话说？",
      "line_start": 1044,
      "line_end": 1044
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我……我没有话说。",
      "line_start": 1046,
      "line_end": 1046
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你不问我为什么忽然要回去？",
      "line_start": 1048,
      "line_end": 1048
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你当然有很好的理由，是不是？",
      "line_start": 1050,
      "line_end": 1050
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "当然，可是……可是你为什么不想法子留住我？",
      "line_start": 1052,
      "line_end": 1052
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我留得住么？",
      "line_start": 1054,
      "line_end": 1054
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "当然留不住，你有什么资格留住我？",
      "line_start": 1056,
      "line_end": 1056
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我并没有要留住你！",
      "line_start": 1058,
      "line_end": 1058
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "对，你并没有要留下我的意思，我为什么还不走呢？我为什么要如此不知趣？",
      "line_start": 1060,
      "line_end": 1060
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我并不是没有要留下你的意思，更没有要你走的意思。",
      "line_start": 1062,
      "line_end": 1062
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "那么你是什么意思？",
      "line_start": 1064,
      "line_end": 1064
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我没有什么意思。",
      "line_start": 1066,
      "line_end": 1066
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你难道是石头？难道不是人？怎么会没有意思？",
      "line_start": 1068,
      "line_end": 1068
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你没有话说了，是不是？",
      "line_start": 1074,
      "line_end": 1074
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "好，你既然连话都不愿跟我说，我不走干什么？",
      "line_start": 1078,
      "line_end": 1078
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我以后永远也不要见你，你若敢来找我，我打死你。",
      "line_start": 1080,
      "line_end": 1082
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我不想回去，你莫要赶我走，我真的不想回去……",
      "line_start": 1128,
      "line_end": 1128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "没有人要赶你走，也没有人能赶你回去。",
      "line_start": 1130,
      "line_end": 1130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你……你醒了。",
      "line_start": 1158,
      "line_end": 1158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "昨天晚上，我又醉得很厉害，是不是？",
      "line_start": 1162,
      "line_end": 1162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "line_start": 1164,
      "line_end": 1164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我醉了之后，一定变得很凶，很不讲理，一定说了很多让你生气的话。",
      "line_start": 1166,
      "line_end": 1166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我不气，因为我知道。",
      "line_start": 1168,
      "line_end": 1168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "知道什么？",
      "line_start": 1170,
      "line_end": 1170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "每个人心里都会有些乱七八糟的烦恼和痛苦，总得找个机会发泄。",
      "line_start": 1172,
      "line_end": 1172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你也有痛苦？",
      "line_start": 1174,
      "line_end": 1174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "本来没有的。",
      "line_start": 1176,
      "line_end": 1176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "难道——难道你认识我之后才有痛苦？",
      "line_start": 1178,
      "line_end": 1178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "line_start": 1180,
      "line_end": 1180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你一定后悔认识我了。",
      "line_start": 1182,
      "line_end": 1182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我不后悔，我很高兴。",
      "line_start": 1184,
      "line_end": 1184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "高兴？我让你痛苦，你却高兴？",
      "line_start": 1186,
      "line_end": 1186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "因为没有痛苦也不会有真正的快乐，我只有跟你在一起的时候，才真正快乐。",
      "line_start": 1188,
      "line_end": 1188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我也一样。",
      "line_start": 1194,
      "line_end": 1194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我现在真的要回去了。",
      "line_start": 1196,
      "line_end": 1196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "line_start": 1198,
      "line_end": 1198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你……你还是不必送我回去。",
      "line_start": 1200,
      "line_end": 1200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我不送。",
      "line_start": 1202,
      "line_end": 1202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "那么我……我走了。",
      "line_start": 1204,
      "line_end": 1204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我也不让你走！",
      "line_start": 1206,
      "line_end": 1206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你不让我走？",
      "line_start": 1208,
      "line_end": 1208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我不让你走！",
      "line_start": 1210,
      "line_end": 1210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "不错，有时我的确想逃避，逃得远远的，可是我非回去不可。",
      "line_start": 1216,
      "line_end": 1216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "line_start": 1218,
      "line_end": 1218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "为什么？我难道还能在这里住一辈子？",
      "line_start": 1220,
      "line_end": 1220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "为什么不能？",
      "line_start": 1222,
      "line_end": 1222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "不能，不能……不能就是不能……",
      "line_start": 1224,
      "line_end": 1224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "放开我——放开我好不好？",
      "line_start": 1232,
      "line_end": 1232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "不好。",
      "line_start": 1234,
      "line_end": 1234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "好，你走……走……",
      "line_start": 1246,
      "line_end": 1246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你……你不必这样做的。",
      "line_start": 1260,
      "line_end": 1260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我不必，可是我愿意，只要你不后悔，我愿意将一切都给你。",
      "line_start": 1262,
      "line_end": 1262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "无论你后不后悔，我绝不后悔，无论以后你怎么样，我现在完全是你的。",
      "line_start": 1264,
      "line_end": 1264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "现在你总该知道我有过别的男人！",
      "line_start": 1296,
      "line_end": 1296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我早已知道。",
      "line_start": 1298,
      "line_end": 1298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你不后悔？",
      "line_start": 1300,
      "line_end": 1300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你……难道你一点也不在乎？",
      "line_start": 1302,
      "line_end": 1302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "过去的事，我为什么要在乎？",
      "line_start": 1304,
      "line_end": 1304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "不管你相信不相信，我都要告诉你，以前我虽然有过别人，但这却是我生平第一次——第一次——",
      "line_start": 1308,
      "line_end": 1308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我相信。",
      "line_start": 1310,
      "line_end": 1310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你听了也许会觉得很可笑，但在我感觉中，我好像还是……还是个处女，好像还是第一次跟男人在一起。",
      "line_start": 1312,
      "line_end": 1312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我明白。",
      "line_start": 1314,
      "line_end": 1314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "那个人是谁？",
      "line_start": 1326,
      "line_end": 1326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你既然不在乎，为什么要问？",
      "line_start": 1328,
      "line_end": 1328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "因为我知道他一定还在纠缠着你。",
      "line_start": 1330,
      "line_end": 1330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你想杀了他？",
      "line_start": 1334,
      "line_end": 1334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我也想杀了他，我早就想杀了他！",
      "line_start": 1344,
      "line_end": 1346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "那么你就该告诉我……",
      "line_start": 1348,
      "line_end": 1348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我不能告诉你。",
      "line_start": 1350,
      "line_end": 1350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "line_start": 1352,
      "line_end": 1352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "因为我不愿你为我去杀人，更不愿你为我去冒险。",
      "line_start": 1354,
      "line_end": 1354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "冒险？",
      "line_start": 1356,
      "line_end": 1356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "他是个很可怕的人，你……你……",
      "line_start": 1358,
      "line_end": 1358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你认为他比我强？……你认为我不是他的对手？",
      "line_start": 1360,
      "line_end": 1362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我没有这意思，绝对没有，只不过……",
      "line_start": 1364,
      "line_end": 1364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "只不过怎样？",
      "line_start": 1366,
      "line_end": 1366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你为什么不说话了？",
      "line_start": 1368,
      "line_end": 1368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我了解。",
      "line_start": 1370,
      "line_end": 1370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我只想让你知道，我现在心里只有你，只关心你，那个人根本不值得你……",
      "line_start": 1386,
      "line_end": 1386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你不用说了，我知道，全都知道。",
      "line_start": 1388,
      "line_end": 1390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你想干什么？",
      "line_start": 1406,
      "line_end": 1406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我……我已出来两三天……",
      "line_start": 1408,
      "line_end": 1408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你想回去？",
      "line_start": 1410,
      "line_end": 1410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "line_start": 1412,
      "line_end": 1412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你一直想回去，一直不肯要我送你，是不是因为那个人在等着你。",
      "line_start": 1414,
      "line_end": 1414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你说你心里只有我，为什么不在这里陪着我？——你心里若是真的只有我，就应该忘了那个人，忘了一切。",
      "line_start": 1418,
      "line_end": 1418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "除非你根本就是骗我的。",
      "line_start": 1420,
      "line_end": 1420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "不错，我根本就是骗你的，我还是想他……",
      "line_start": 1424,
      "line_end": 1426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "我既然已对你说明白了，你为什么还要死皮赖脸地拉住我？",
      "line_start": 1430,
      "line_end": 1430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你打我……原来你也打女人！",
      "line_start": 1441,
      "line_end": 1442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "我既然打了你，你为什么还不走？",
      "line_start": 1462,
      "line_end": 1462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你虽然不该打我，可是我……我也不该故意气你。",
      "line_start": 1464,
      "line_end": 1464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "你是故意气我的？",
      "line_start": 1466,
      "line_end": 1466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你难道真的相信我在骗你？我为什么要骗你？",
      "line_start": 1468,
      "line_end": 1468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "text": "不错，你为什么要骗我？我有什么值得你骗的……我简直不是个东西。",
      "line_start": 1470,
      "line_end": 1470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "text": "你的确不是东西……你是个人。",
      "line_start": 1472,
      "line_end": 1474
    }
  ],
  "dialogue_count": 157
}